trans-unit.resname: Runalyze is completely configurable and more detailed than any other tool for analyzing your activities.
trans-unit.source: Runalyze is completely configurable and more detailed than any other tool for analyzing your activities.
trans-unit.target: Runalyze est totalement paramétrable et plus détaillé que n'importe quel autre outil pour analyser vos activités.

trans-unit.resname: Please look at our official website %s to get an overview of our features.
trans-unit.source: Please look at our official website %s to get an overview of our features.
trans-unit.target: Veuillez vous reporter à notre site web officiel %s afin d'avoir un aperçu des fonctionnalités.

trans-unit.resname: If you want to stay up to date on changes and receive tips from time to time, visit our blog at %s.
trans-unit.source: If you want to stay up to date on changes and receive tips from time to time, visit our blog at %s.
trans-unit.target: Si vous souhaitez rester à jour sur les améliorations et recevoir des astuces de temps en temps, rendez-vous sur notre blog à l'adresse %s.

trans-unit.resname: Runalyze is an open-source project. We are working on it as much as we can in our free time.
trans-unit.source: Runalyze is an open-source project. We are working on it as much as we can in our free time.
trans-unit.target: Runalyze est un projet open-source. Nous travaillons autant que possible sur notre temps libre.

trans-unit.resname: The main advantage of Runalyze is the ability to adapt everything to your personal needs and wishes.
trans-unit.source: The main advantage of Runalyze is the ability to adapt everything to your personal needs and wishes.
trans-unit.target: Le principal avantage de Runalyze est sa capacité d'adaptation complète à vos propres besoins et envies.

trans-unit.resname: Have a look at the configuration window to see what we're talking about.
trans-unit.source: Have a look at the configuration window to see what we're talking about.
trans-unit.target: Jeter un œil à la fenêtre de configuration pour voir de quoi nous parlons.

trans-unit.resname: You can define your own sports or activity types and choose your own way of presentation and configure some parameters of our experimental calculations.
trans-unit.source: You can define your own sports or activity types and choose your own way of presentation and configure some parameters of our experimental calculations.
trans-unit.target: Vous pouvez définir vos propres sports ou types d'activité, personnaliser la présentation et configurer certains paramètres expérimentaux de calcul.

trans-unit.resname: Please let us know if you have wishes or have encountered bugs.
trans-unit.source: Please let us know if you have wishes or have encountered bugs.
trans-unit.target: Merci de nous faire part de vos souhaits ou de nous faire un retour en cas de bug.

trans-unit.resname: We give our best to make Runalyze as good as possible for you. - Therefore we would be interested in your suggestions for improvement.
trans-unit.source: We give our best to make Runalyze as good as possible for you. - Therefore we would be interested in your suggestions for improvement.
trans-unit.target: Nous faisons tout notre possible pour vous garantir la meilleure expérience avec Runalyze. Nous sommes donc toujours intéressés par vos suggestions d'amélioration.

trans-unit.resname: In general most questions, problems and ideas are more appropriate to ask in the forum.
trans-unit.source: In general most questions, problems and ideas are more appropriate to ask in the forum.
trans-unit.target: Le forum est généralement plus adapté pour discuter de vos questions, problèmes et idées.

trans-unit.resname: Runalyze is a modern application and therefore we want to use the most modern web techniques. We will not try to support any outdated browser versions.

trans-unit.resname: Runalyze analyzes your complete training, calculates your shape, computes prognoses and visualizes your training in plots - more detailed than any other sports diary.
trans-unit.source: Runalyze analyzes your complete training, calculates your shape, computes prognoses and visualizes your training in plots - more detailed than any other sports diary.
trans-unit.target: Runalyze analyse l'ensemble de votre entraînement, évalue votre forme, calcule des prévisions et permet de visualiser l'entraînement via des graphiques, plus complet que n'importe quel carnet de sport.

trans-unit.resname: Runalyze is completely configurable. You can decide by yourself which information of your training you want to record and which statistics are being displayed on which place.
trans-unit.source: Runalyze is completely configurable. You can decide by yourself which information of your training you want to record and which statistics are being displayed on which place.
trans-unit.target: Runalyze est entièrement paramétrable. Vous choisissez vous-même quelles données d'entraînement vous souhaitez enregistrer et quelles statistiques doivent être affichées à quel endroit.

trans-unit.resname: Runalyze is created by athletes for athletes. Whenever you have comments, problems or wishes: Please contact our Runalyze team. It's near and dear to us.
